sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant LB as Load Balancer
    participant MW as Middleware Stack
    participant Auth as Authentication
    participant Router as API Router
    participant Service as Business Service
    participant CRUD as CRUD Layer
    participant DB as Database
    participant AI as AI Services
    participant Search as Search Service
    
    Note over Client,Search: Request Processing Flow
    
    Client->>LB: HTTP Request
    LB->>MW: Forward Request
    
    Note over MW: Middleware Processing
    MW->>MW: ProxyHeadersMiddleware
    MW->>MW: CORSMiddleware
    MW->>MW: SessionMiddleware
    MW->>MW: LoggingContextMiddleware
    MW->>MW: UserActivityMiddleware
    
    MW->>Auth: Authentication Check
    Auth->>Auth: Validate JWT Token
    Auth->>DB: Lookup User
    DB-->>Auth: User Data
    Auth-->>MW: Authenticated User
    
    MW->>Router: Route Request
    Router->>Service: Business Logic Call
    
    alt AI-Enhanced Operation
        Service->>AI: AI Service Call
        AI->>Search: Vector Search
        Search-->>AI: Search Results
        AI-->>Service: AI Response
    end
    
    Service->>CRUD: Data Operation
    CRUD->>DB: SQL Query
    DB-->>CRUD: Query Result
    CRUD-->>Service: Data Model
    
    Service-->>Router: Business Result
    Router-->>MW: HTTP Response
    MW-->>LB: Processed Response
    LB-->>Client: Final Response
    
    Note over Client,Search: Error Handling Flow
    
    alt Error Scenario
        Service->>Service: Error Occurs
        Service->>Service: Log Error
        Service-->>Router: HTTP Exception
        Router-->>MW: Error Response
        MW-->>Client: Error Response
    end